    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Shallow drinking cups or bowls, with curved sides and flattened bases, typically made from forest glass. Often decorated with ribs or moderately high bosses or prunts.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
